{
  "text": "A similar result also holds for \u03bb > 1, but in that case the the limiting distribution has an additional point mass of 1\u22121/\u03bb at the origin. A straightforward proof of the Marchenko-Pastur law using the Stieltjes transform is given in Chapter 3 of [CITATION_1] . More extensive expositions of the Marchenko-Pastur law with proofs using both the moment method and the Stieltjes transform are given in [CITATION_2] Chapter 3] and [CITATION_3] . Furthermore, [CITATION_4] includes a review of many existing works prior to 1999. ",
  "correct_citation": {
